- I have an extension that evaluates some selected text in node in the terminal
- As soon as I select the terminal (click) its content scroll up and I cannot get it back

![sep-01-2016 12-35-53](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1794099/18164541/b7b4b32e-7040-11e6-9f14-e5ce4b122383.gif)

``` js
    let terminal: vscode.Terminal;
    vscode.commands.registerCommand('extension.runInNode', () => {
        let {selection, document} = vscode.window.activeTextEditor;
        let text = document.getText(selection);

        if (!terminal) {
            terminal = vscode.window.createTerminal({ name: 'nodejs - scratch page'});
        }

        terminal.sendText('node');
        terminal.sendText(text);

    });
```

